race.comment: Tricky race to end the night. LUNAR LOVER (10) lightly raced stayer heading in the right direction third-up. Ready for the 1900m now after chipping away late with the 60kg when fifth over 1600m at Warwick Farm. Gets map favours and will take holding out. LIBERTY PARK (3) back in grade and at his top for this. Will appreciate Grima's 3kg claim and doesn't have to improve much after finishing a narrow third over this course and distance at latest. No excuses from the low draw. DE LOUVIERE (20) strengthened up over the break and looking for this trip and further at his third run back. Strong through the line when third over 1600m at Gosford. Zac Lloyd retains the ride and can take a hand in the finish.
